VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'least take up complex activities and I know people are going to want to say that plants are not intelligent, they\'re just doing mechanistic things. I\'m not entirely sure that I\'m not, okay? I am fascinated by how C. elegans managed to turn memories into something'

